<div class="intro">
<div class="welcome">
Welcome to ECS, the School  of Electronics and Computer Science at the University of Southampton. ECS is one of the world's leading centres for 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/research/">research</a>, 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/about/teaching/">teaching</a>, <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/business/">enterprise and innovation</a> in Electronics, Electrical Engineering and Computer Science.
<div class="sig">Head of School: <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/people/wh">Professor Wendy Hall</a></div>
</div>
<div class="headline"><a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/697"><img src="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006im_/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/image.php?id=news_697_img&amp;maxw=200&amp;maxh=150&amp;corners=10&amp;edge=1&amp;checksum=9f4b9b1182af986def319019bc1de32d&amp;fn=fn.png" alt="Professor Wendy Hall and Professor Jintong Lin" title="Professor Wendy Hall and Professor Jintong Lin (Copyright: ECS)" border="0" width="200" height="150" class="thumbnail" /></a><h2>Headline News</h2><h3><a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050311095006/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/697">Professor Jintong Lin named 'Distinguished Alumnus' of ECS</a></h3><p>ECS graduate Professor Jintong Lin has been named 'Distinguished Alumnus' of the School.</p><p>Professor Wendy Hall, Head of the School of Electronics and Computer Science, presented Professor Lin with a framed certificate when she visited China to conclude a formal agreement with the Beijing University of Posts and Telecommunications (BUPT) of which Professor Lin is President. BUPT will now send up to 20 students each year on the new ECS MSc programme in Software Engineering.</p></div></div><div class='rightside'>

